# Prisma / database

Canonical rationale: `docs/DATABASE.md`. Patterns: skill `prisma-patterns`.

## Same-task hygiene

Any `prisma/schema.prisma` change must include in the same task:

1. A Prisma migration
2. Update `docs/DATABASE.md`
3. A `docs/CHANGELOG.md` entry

## Conventions

- IDs: `cuid()` except `User.id` (Clerk user ID).
- Money: `Decimal(10,2)` EGP.
- No soft-delete — products use `status = ARCHIVED`; users use `active = false`.
- Choose `Cascade` / `Restrict` / `SetNull` deliberately per `docs/DATABASE.md` §1.

## Stock

All stock mutations use the conditional-decrement transaction in `docs/ADR-0003-stock-reservation-strategy.md`. Never read-then-write stock.
